{"tid":201342,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)咒怨1-2","createTime":"2017-04-14T16:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T19:25:23.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"208ccea1432cc72900ee656ef40fc044fd58f056","tid":201342,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T16:15:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2F&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=741780d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/</a> CC台執柒左<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=03322cbb\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/14e0007a1e41145abbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2F14e0007a1e41145abbc.jpg&h=f7233771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.東京近郊一間屋被傳是陰森鬼屋，說但凡拜訪者進入，都會離奇斃命或神秘失踪。傳說當年該屋的主人曾因突至的狂性大發斬死妻子，爾後自殺，其6歲的兒子從此失踪，至今下落不明，鬼屋自此怨氣沖天，每一位到訪者都會在瞬間被恐怖籠罩。<br />\n　　大學女生理佳（奧菜惠）因做義工無意間闖入該屋，在遍尋不著要照顧的老人後，她於無意間瞥見一個神秘詭異男孩，但轉眼男孩又失踪。自此，諸多恐怖怪事開始接二連三在理佳身上發生，其身邊的親朋好友也一一受到牽連..<br />\n<br />\n2.午夜，一輛私家車在日本東京的一條高速公路上疾馳。車裡是一個美麗的女子原瀨京子（酒井法子 飾），她是著名的恐怖電影演員，人稱&quot;恐怖女王&quot;。這天夜晚，在友情出演《被詛咒的一家》這一電視節目後，她坐上了未婚夫石倉將志的車返回家中。正當他們行駛在高速公路上時，突然間，聽到&quot;咚&quot;的一聲響，一個黑影從前方閃過，他們趕緊剎車，但還是把橫穿馬路的貓給撞死了..<br />\n<br />\n12 40AM左右播了 隨時嚇到電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返V台睇炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fee9cab7331853a065f707ffc93047cca0e2009","tid":201342,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T16:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9395520aee0342dfa86a7df18cd7ec308cfadec1","tid":201342,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf087eda5d0af9ae41390435590dd6831029f7f1","tid":201342,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6297e1d6de21ce199e8f3f677dcefec733d9b02","tid":201342,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b320d5b258e8cbd57a221ab9807d0ff4ec05f456","tid":201342,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891aa6a166c3c629cc0c40db3cf6d80cc77b6844","tid":201342,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:57:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6937adbf9e67b0c99ad3aee0703db22f00165e6b","tid":201342,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T19:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}